SEARCH
Package aas_core.aas3_0.visitation

Interface ITransformer<T>

Type Parameters:
T - type of the transformation result
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractTransformer
public interface ITransformer<T>
Define the interface for a transformer which transforms recursively the instances into something else.

When you use the transformer, please always call the main dispatching method transform(aas_core.aas3_0.types.model.IClass). You should most probably never call the transform methods directly. They are only made public so that model classes can access them.
